==Description==
The '''Star Piece''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The Star Piece has a value of 5 Diamonds {{Diamonds}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals. 

==Mine Layout==
The Star Piece appears in the Underground as a 3x3 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:StarPieceMine.png|100px]]

==Acquisition==
Star Pieces can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], as [[Rare Hold Items]] from [[File:Jirachi.png|30px]] Jirachi, and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

